### D. Naming Conventions

| Artifact | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Component selector | `app-` prefix + kebab-case | `app-user-card` |
| Component class | PascalCase + `Component` suffix | `UserCardComponent` |
| Service class | PascalCase + `Service` suffix | `UsersService` |
| Interface | PascalCase, no prefix | `User`, `GridColumnConfig` |
| Type alias | PascalCase | `UserRole`, `SortDirection` |
| Signal | camelCase noun | `selectedUser`, `isLoading`, `pageTitle` |
| Computed signal | camelCase noun (no `get` prefix) | `filteredUsers`, `totalCount` |
| Event handler method | `on` + PascalCase action | `onUserSelect`, `onFilterChange`, `onSave` |
| Private method | camelCase | `loadData`, `buildGridColumns` |
| CSS class (BEM block) | feature name | `.user-card` |
| CSS class (BEM element) | `__element` | `.user-card__avatar` |
| CSS class (BEM modifier) | `--modifier` | `.user-card--compact` |
| CSS variable | kebab-case semantic | `--color-sf-primary`, `--spacing-md` |
| File name | kebab-case matching selector | `user-card.component.ts` |
| Route path | kebab-case | `/user-management/create` |

