### F. Shared Components — Required for Every Product

These shared components must exist in `shared/components/` in every Khwarizmi product:

| Component | Selector | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Empty state | `app-empty-state` | Standardized empty state with icon, title, description, CTA |
| Confirm dialog | `app-confirm-dialog` | Wraps `ejs-dialog` Confirm — used for all destructive actions |
| Page header | `app-page-header` | Page title + breadcrumb + page-level actions |
| Status badge | `app-status-badge` | `ejs-badge` or `ejs-chip` mapped from status enum → color |
| Skeleton card | `app-skeleton-card` | Composed `ejs-skeleton` blocks for card loading states |
| Toast service | `ToastService` | Service wrapping `ejs-toast` — `showSuccess()`, `showError()`, `showWarning()` |

```typescript
// shared/components/empty-state/empty-state.component.ts
export class EmptyStateComponent {
  @Input() icon = 'e-icons e-folder-open';
  @Input() title = 'لا توجد بيانات';
  @Input() description = '';
  @Input() actionLabel = '';
  @Output() action = new EventEmitter<void>();
  readonly hasAction = computed(() => !!this.actionLabel);
}
```

```typescript
// shared/services/toast.service.ts
@Injectable({ providedIn: 'root' })
export class ToastService {
  private toastRef: ToastComponent | null = null;

  register(toast: ToastComponent): void { this.toastRef = toast; }

  showSuccess(message: string): void {
    this.toastRef?.show({ content: message, cssClass: 'e-toast-success' });
  }

  showError(message: string): void {
    this.toastRef?.show({ content: message, cssClass: 'e-toast-danger' });
  }

  showWarning(message: string): void {
    this.toastRef?.show({ content: message, cssClass: 'e-toast-warning' });
  }
}
```

