### H. Quality Gates

Run this checklist before outputting any Angular artifact.

**Architecture:**
- [ ] All components are standalone with `ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush`
- [ ] No `any` types — zero tolerance
- [ ] All data shapes have interfaces in a `models/` file
- [ ] Business logic is in a service, not the component
- [ ] Components are under size limits (150 lines template, 120 lines TS logic)
- [ ] No duplicated code — extracted to shared components or services

**Syncfusion:**
- [ ] Every UI element mapped to a Syncfusion component (or explicitly justified)
- [ ] Syncfusion modules imported in the component's `imports[]` array
- [ ] Grid components have required service providers
- [ ] `[property]` binding used — not HTML attributes

**Styling:**
- [ ] No hardcoded colors, spacing, or font sizes
- [ ] All values use `--color-sf-*`, `--spacing-*`, or other token variables
- [ ] No inline `style=""` attributes
- [ ] `::ng-deep` scoped inside `:host`
- [ ] Logical CSS properties used (`padding-inline-start` not `padding-left`)

**RTL & Localization:**
- [ ] `enableRtl(true)` set in `main.ts`
- [ ] `<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">` on root element
- [ ] No manual `direction: rtl` on individual components
- [ ] Arabic locale loaded via `L10n.load()`

**Accessibility:**
- [ ] Icon-only buttons have `aria-label`
- [ ] Form fields have labels (visible or `aria-label`)
- [ ] No `tabindex` overrides on Syncfusion components
- [ ] Syncfusion ARIA attributes not removed
- [ ] Skip link present in shell layout

**Responsiveness:**
- [ ] Layout works at 375px, 600px, 1024px, 1440px
- [ ] No fixed pixel widths on content containers
- [ ] Sidebar collapses on tablet, hides on mobile
- [ ] Touch targets ≥ 44×44px

**Code Quality:**
- [ ] No `console.log` in final output
- [ ] No commented-out code blocks
- [ ] Lazy-loaded routes — no eager feature imports
- [ ] `takeUntilDestroyed` on all RxJS subscriptions in components

---

### I. Do / Don't Summary

**Do:**
- ✅ Follow the project structure exactly — no ad-hoc folders
- ✅ One feature = one folder under `features/`
- ✅ Shared components in `shared/` — feature components in `features/`
- ✅ `core/` for singletons only (auth, HTTP, shell layout)
- ✅ Match file names to selector names exactly
- ✅ Run the quality gate checklist before every output

**Don't:**
- ❌ Do not put components in `app/` root — they belong in `core/`, `shared/`, or `features/`
- ❌ Do not import one feature's components into another feature
- ❌ Do not put HTTP calls in components
- ❌ Do not create top-level barrel files (`index.ts`) in features — use direct imports
- ❌ Do not store derived data in a signal when `computed()` would do the job
- ❌ Do not create empty folders as placeholders
